{"tid":522642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 詠 琪 囡 囡 Sofia 最 愛 穿 花 裙 甜 美 似 公 仔","createTime":"2018-01-07T17:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T19:33:11.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"954c120e070d4a60e48c812bbdf48ca415bee4be","tid":522642,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（Gigi)的混血囡囡Sofia 精靈又可愛，眼大大的她被指同「怪獸公司」入面的阿Boo撞樣，cute 到似公仔，而Sofia 着起花裙時更是甜美。<br />\n<br />\n日前Gigi 帶埋囡囡去海港城食點心，扎起孖辮的Sofia 着上西班牙童裝品牌Nanos 今季最新春裝的花花連身裙，可愛程度滿分，更似乎遺傳左媽咪「高妹」的基因，比同齡的小朋友生得更高，又靚又得意。<br />\n<br />\n而Gigi 之前就提過雖然Sofia 喜歡公主裙，但唔會買畀囡囡，不過看來買左唔少花裙，之前出席活動時就曾着過Dolce &amp; Gabbana 的花裙，非常適合甜美的Sofia！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180105/large/1515146546_a277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180105%2Flarge%2F1515146546_a277.jpg&h=9582b955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb919a0d9c96a98cca0bce91342473ddd44e7bf6","tid":522642,"uid":139815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T17:50:36.000Z","msg":"肥媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebc161fb60e37d9083269f0c9dd3c1f6da5d085","tid":522642,"uid":65893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:22:10.000Z","msg":"咁醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe10e0a5dc76469b4bce21f1367748e540b7b48","tid":522642,"uid":80176,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:23:20.000Z","msg":"同邵美琪撞樣就真"},{"pid":"dcaea1461fddfb6302bf54240d799a5318a4f65a","tid":522642,"uid":36029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T19:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 梁詠琪（Gigi)與西班牙藉老公Sergio的混血囡囡Sofia 精靈又可愛，眼大大的她被指同「怪獸公司」入面的阿Boo撞樣，cute 到似公仔，而西班牙藉老公Sergio的混血囡囡Sofia 着起花裙時更是甜美。<br />\n<br />\n日前Gigi 帶埋囡囡去海港城食點心，扎起孖辮的西班牙藉老公Sergio的混血囡囡Sofia 着上西班牙童裝品牌Nanos 今季最新春裝的花花連身裙，可愛程度滿分，更似乎遺傳左媽咪「高妹」的基因，比同齡的小朋友生得更高，又靚又得意。<br />\n<br />\n而Gigi 之前就提過雖然西班牙藉老公Sergio的混血囡囡Sofia 喜歡公主裙，但唔會買畀囡囡，不過看來買左唔少花裙，之前出席活動時就曾着過Dolce &amp; Gabbana 的花裙，非常適合甜美的西班牙藉老公Sergio的混血囡囡Sofia！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180105/large/1515146546_a277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180105%2Flarge%2F1515146546_a277.jpg&h=9582b955&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}